Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.21,0:00:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,這也太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.54,0:00:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不能放著不管
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.32,0:00:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,但是沒時間救所有人了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.65,0:00:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡 該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.64,0:00:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,車站在…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.58,0:00:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,五條老師明明都那麼近了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.18,0:00:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,明太子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.38,0:00:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,這個詞是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.03,0:00:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,狗卷學長
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.39,0:00:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,鮭魚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.06,0:00:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託你了
